org.netbeans.spi.viewmodel

Interface NodeModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Model
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CheckNodeModel, DnDNodeModel, ExtendedNodeModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Models.CompoundModel

    public interface NodeModel
extends Model
    Provides display name, icon and tool tip value for some type of objects. Designed to be used with TreeModel.
